body.description: Features: This router resets the power cord, has a built-in programmed timer and smart controller that automatically reboots your wifi router or other network device every 72 hours and repeats the cycle. Due to memory problems, long-term operation of the router will cause a large amount of data to be cached. After restarting the wireless router, it will empty its memory, let the system run again, and improve the network speed. No need to set up, plug and for play, just connect router rebooter to your router and you can use it, Calculated from the for time you use it, the router will automatically restart within 72 hours. It supports all for 5V 9V 12V 15V for devices, such as: routers, Fiber Modem, optical cats, Lamp speakers and more. Specifications: Support for 5V~15V for equipment Connector type: for 5.5x2.5mm female, for 5.5x2.5mm male Restart interval: 5 to 15 seconds Timing time: Automatic power off cycle restart every 72 hours from the start of the device Cabel Length:60cm/23.6inch Package: 2x dc 5525 Extension Cable with Router Rebooter ( 1xblack + 1xwhite )
